This is a preliminary implementation of a converter from RIF BLD 
(abstract syntax and concrete XML syntax) to the TPTP format (abstract and 
concrete syntax ) for first-order predicate logic. 


No formula names are supported yet. 

Data literals are supported in a way which may not optimal.

The conversion is rigid now -- parameters will be added later.


"ant javadoc" to create API documentation (./docs/api/index.html).


Usage example:

java -enableassertions -cp ./lib/getopt.jar:./lib/TptpParser.jar:./lib/RIF_BLD_AbstractSyntax.jar:./lib/RIF_BLD_Parser.jar:./build/jar/RIF_BLD_to_TPTP.jar rif.bld.totptp.RIF_BLD_to_TPTP -p sample_parameters.xml -a accumulated_parameters.xml ./tests/test2.rif

